<body>

<p>The PNG images, which are contained in a object element, have

been assigned the HSPACE attribute. HSPACE adds white space to left

and right sides of the image. The first image has been assigned a

value of 80 pixels; the second image has been assign 140

pixels.</p>



<object data="../images/trucks.png" type="image/png" hspace="80">A

maze graphic should be displayed.</object> HSPACE adds white space

to left and right sides of the image. The graphic to the left of

this paragraph has HSPACE set to 80 pixels. <br />

 <object data="../images/trucks.png" hspace="140">A maze graphic

should be displayed.</object> HSPACE adds white space to left and

right sides of the image. The graphic to the left of this paragraph

has HSPACE set to 140 pixels. 

